<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('./partials/head.ejs', {
    pageTitle: "About | BookLantern",
    pageDescription: "Learn what BookLantern is and how it offers free access to books, documentaries, and educational content."
  }) %>
  <style>
    :root { --bg:#f6f7fb; --text:#111; --muted:#667085; --link:#1256b3; --card:#fff; --border:#e5e7eb; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 880px;
      margin: 2rem auto 3rem;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.2vw, 2.5rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .highlight { color: var(--link); font-weight: 600; }
    .back-home {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--link);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .back-home:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>About BookLantern</h1>
      <p>
        <span class="highlight">BookLantern</span> is your free gateway to a world of knowledge and stories.
        We connect readers and learners with an expansive archive of books and documentaries — at zero cost.
      </p>
      <p>
        We believe access to knowledge should be barrier-free. BookLantern fetches open-access and public-domain
        books from trusted sources and presents them in a clean reading experience, without hassle.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you’re exploring timeless classics, academic materials, or diving into documentaries on our Watch page,
        BookLantern supports your curiosity.
      </p>
      <p>
        Create a free account to save favorites, track your progress, and enjoy new educational content added regularly.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Your lantern to the world of knowledge starts here.</strong></p>

      <a href="/" class="back-home">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
